MindMaestro.introText.defaultMessage: Mind Maestro is an interactive quiz where you get your unique username based on your answers to 5 targeted questions.

MindMaestro.introText2.defaultMessage: Each question aims to explore specific preferences, interests, or personality traits. At the end of the quiz, a suitable username will be generated based on your answers, reflecting your individual personality.

MindMaestro.introText3.defaultMessage: Be surprised and discover your personal Mind Maestro name!

identityWizard.text.defaultMessage: Create a unique username by selecting up to two groups of adjectives and a group of nouns, or let the generator create a random combination for you.

landing-cta-text.defaultMessage: Discover now how easy it is to increase your security!

landing-lead-text.defaultMessage: Say goodbye to boring passwords and usernames!

landing-sub-lead-text.defaultMessage: Optimize your passwords and usernames with our tools. Test their strength, create new secure options, and find the perfect online name.

passwordGenerating.glyphSorcery.descript.defaultMessage: The longer your password, the more secure it is. With Glyph Sorcery, you can quickly and easily create a password in your desired length that meets secure password guidelines.

passwordGenerating.pictureMagic.pictureT.defaultMessage: Simply upload a photo, and our app will turn it into a secure password

passwordTesting.excalibur.benefits.defaultMessage: By using Excalibur, you can strengthen your password protection and improve your security.

passwordTesting.excalibur.description.defaultMessage: Excalibur is a tool that checks the strength of your password. It evaluates factors like length, complexity, and predictability and provides you with a comprehensive assessment of your password security.

passwordTesting.excalibur.howItWorks.defaultMessage: With this tool, you can ensure that your password is well protected against brute-force attacks and common password lists.

passwordTesting.mojo.textContent.defaultMessage: Choose a mode to test your password against brute-force attacks. In the

passwordTesting.mojo.textContent.descrip.defaultMessage: Both modes help you assess the strength of your password and uncover potential vulnerabilities

passwordTesting.mojo.textContent.recomme.defaultMessage: Choose the mode that best suits your security needs to effectively protect your passwords.

runeText-description.defaultMessage: Leetspeak is a type of text transformation where certain letters and characters are replaced by others. Try it out to better protect your password.
